To create 'egp_scribe.exe' from 'egp_scribe.py':

    1) install pyinstaller
        from command line, execute the following
            pip3 install pyinstaller
        then close command line
        
    2) open command line terminal from folder where you've saved 'egp_scribe.py'
    
    3) run the following from the command line
        pyinstaller -F egp_scribe.py
    
    When process is complete, exe will be located in the 'dist' folder. 

(egp_scribe.exe is not included in this GitHub repo strictly because of file size limitations)
